description: Retrieves the history of all changes to a parameter.

parameters.name: Name
parameters.description: The name or Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the parameter for which you want to review history. For parameters shared with you from another account, you must use the full ARN.

nested_items.name: Parameters
nested_items.description: A list of parameters returned by the request.

nested_items.name: KeyId
nested_items.description: The alias of the Key Management Service (KMS) key used to encrypt the parameter. Applies to SecureString parameters only.

nested_items.name: LastModifiedDate
nested_items.description: Date the parameter was last changed or updated.

nested_items.name: LastModifiedUser
nested_items.description: Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the Amazon Web Services user who last changed the parameter.

nested_items.name: AllowedPattern
nested_items.description: Parameter names can include the following letters and symbols.

nested_items.name: Labels
nested_items.description: Labels assigned to the parameter version.

nested_items.name: Policies
nested_items.description: Information about the policies assigned to a parameter.

nested_items.name: PolicyText
nested_items.description: The JSON text of the policy.

nested_items.name: PolicyType
nested_items.description: The type of policy. Parameter Store, a tool in Amazon Web Services Systems Manager, supports the following policy types: Expiration, ExpirationNotification, and NoChangeNotification.

nested_items.name: PolicyStatus
nested_items.description: The status of the policy. Policies report the following statuses: Pending (the policy hasn't been enforced or applied yet), Finished (the policy was applied), Failed (the policy wasn't applied), or InProgress (the policy is being applied now).

nested_items.name: DataType
nested_items.description: The data type of the parameter, such as text or aws:ec2:image. The default is text.

nested_items.name: NextToken
nested_items.description: The token to use when requesting the next set of items. If there are no additional items to return, the string is empty.
